message  "${DISPEL_COLOR}If you are using the nVidia binary graphics driver"
message  "older than 302.17, you need to use --force-xinerama (in your .xsession)"
message  "when starting i3, like so:"
message  "exec i3 --force-xinerama -V >>~/.i3/i3log 2>&1"
message  "or use ${DEFAULT_COLOR}force_xinerama yes${DISPEL_COLOR} in your configuration file.${DEFAULT_COLOR}"
